item.title: New Jersey Transit issues warning for riders ahead of potential rail strike
item.description: New Jersey Transit is urging riders to reach their destinations or risk being stranded. The warning comes as talks continued Thursday in a bid to avert a rail strike by train engineers that would affect some 350,000 commuters who work in New Jersey and New York City.
